\c 28
\s Iminikelo enikelwa insuku ngensuku, lenikelwa izinyanga ngezinyanga, lenikelwa emikhosini
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Laya abantwana bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo: Umnikelo wami, isinkwa sami seminikelo eyenziwe ngomlilo\x + Levi 3.11.\x*, uqhatshi lwami olumnandi, lizakuqaphela ukukunikela kimi ngesikhathi sakho esimisiweyo.
\v 3 Uzakuthi kibo: Lo ngumnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo elizawunikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Eks. 29.38.\x*; amawundlu amabili alomnyaka owodwa, angelasici, insuku ngensuku, kube ngumnikelo wokutshiswa njalonjalo.
\v 4 Elinye iwundlu uzalilungisa ekuseni, lelinye iwundlu ulinikele kusihlwa,
\v 5 lokwetshumi \w kwe-efa\w** lempuphu ecolekileyo\x + Eks. 16.36. Nani 15.4.\x* kube ngumnikelo wokudla\x + Levi 2.1.\x*, kuxubene lengxenye yesine \w yehini\w** yamafutha agigiweyo\x + Eks. 29.40.\x*.
\v 6 Kungumnikelo wokutshiswa wezikhathi zonke\x + Eks. 29.42. Amos 5.25.\x* owamiswa entabeni yeSinayi, ube luqhatshi olumnandi, umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\v 7 Lomnikelo wawo wokunathwayo uzakuba yingxenye yesine yehini ngewundlu linye; uzathululela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni umnikelo wokunathwayo \add ongo\add*wokunathwayo okulamandla endaweni engcwele\x + Eks. 29.42.\x*.
\v 8 Lelinye iwundlu uzalilungisa kusihlwa; njengomnikelo wokudla wekuseni, lanjengomnikelo wawo wokunathwayo uzalinikela, umnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo, oloqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\p
\v 9 Langosuku lwesabatha amawundlu amabili, alomnyaka owodwa, angelasici, lengxenye ezimbili zetshumi lempuphu ecolekileyo, kube ngumnikelo wokudla, ixubene lamafutha, lomnikelo wawo wokunathwayo;
\v 10 kungumnikelo wokutshiswa wamasabatha wonke\x + Hez. 46.4,5.\x*, ngaphandle komnikelo wokutshiswa wezikhathi zonke, lomnikelo wawo wokunathwayo.
\p
\v 11 Ekuqaleni kwenyanga zenu lizanikela umnikelo wokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 10.10. 1 Sam. 20.5. 1 Lan. 23.31. 2 Lan. 2.4. Ezra 3.5. Neh. 10.33. Isa. 1.13,14. Hez. 45.17. 46.6. Hos. 2.11. Kol. 2.16.\x*, amajongosi amabili amathole enkomo, lenqama eyodwa, lamawundlu ayisikhombisa alomnyaka owodwa, angelasici,
\v 12 lengxenye ezintathu zetshumi lempuphu ecolekileyo kube ngumnikelo wokudla, ixubene lamafutha, ngejongosi elilodwa\x + 15.4-12.\x*; lokubili kwetshumi kwempuphu ecolekileyo kube ngumnikelo wokudla, ixubene lamafutha, ngenqama eyodwa,
\v 13 njalo yilokho lalokho okwetshumi kwempuphu ecolekileyo kuxubene lamafutha kube ngumnikelo wokudla ngewundlu elilodwa; ngumnikelo wokutshiswa oloqhatshi olumnandi, umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\v 14 Leminikelo yayo yokunathwayo izakuba yingxenye yehini lewayini ngejongosi, lengxenye yesithathu yehini ngenqama, lengxenye yesine yehini ngewundlu. Lokhu kungumnikelo wokutshiswa wezinyanga zonke ngezinyanga zomnyaka.
\v 15 Futhi kuzalungiswa izinyane lembuzi elilodwa libe ngumnikelo wesono eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 28.30.15.24. 29.11,16,19,25,32.\x*, ngaphandle komnikelo wokutshiswa ngezikhathi zonke, lomnikelo wawo wokunathwayo.
\p
\v 16 Futhi ngenyanga yokuqala ngosuku lwetshumi lane lwenyanga kuliphasika leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Eks. 12.6. Dute. 16.1. Hez. 45.21.\x*.
\v 17 Langosuku lwetshumi lanhlanu lwenyanga le kuzakuba khona umkhosi\x + Levi 23.6. Eks. 12.18.\x*; kuzadliwa isinkwa esingelamvubelo insuku eziyisikhombisa.
\v 18 Ngosuku lokuqala kuzakuba khona inhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele\x + Eks. 12.16. Levi 23.7.\x*; lingenzi lamsebenzi wezisebenzi,
\v 19 kodwa lizanikela umnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo, umnikelo wokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, amajongosi amabili amathole enkomo, lenqama eyodwa, lamawundlu ayisikhombisa alomnyaka owodwa; kuzakuba ngokungelasici kini\x + 28.31. Levi 22.20. Nani 29.8,13. Levi 22.20. Nani 29.2,17,20,23,26,29,32,36. Dute. 15.21. 17.1.\x*.
\v 20 Lomnikelo wakho wokudla kuzakuba yimpuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha; okuthathu kwetshumi lizakulungisa ngejongosi, lokubili kwetshumi ngenqama,
\v 21 yilokho lalokho okwetshumi uzakulungiselela iwundlu elilodwa, kumawundlu ayisikhombisa;
\v 22 lempongo eyodwa ibe ngumnikelo wesono, ukulenzela inhlawulo yokuthula\x + 28.15,30. 29.22,28,31,34,38.\x*.
\v 23 Lizalungisa lokho ngaphandle komnikelo wokutshiswa wekuseni, ongowomnikelo wokutshiswa wezikhathi zonke.
\v 24 Ngalindlela lizalungisa insuku zonke, okwensuku eziyisikhombisa\x + 28.3.\x*, ukudla komnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo, uqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; kuzanikelwa ngaphandle komnikelo wokutshiswa wezikhathi zonke, lomnikelo wawo wokunathwayo.
\v 25 Langosuku lwesikhombisa lizakuba lenhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele\x + Eks. 12.16. Levi 23.8. Eks. 13.6.\x*; lingenzi lamsebenzi wezisebenzi.
\p
\v 26 Langosuku lwezithelo zokuqala\x + Eks. 23.16. 34.22. Levi 23.10,15. Dute. 16.10. Seb. 2.1.\x*, lapho liletha umnikelo wokudla omutsha eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, emavikini enu, lizakuba lenhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele; lingenzi lamsebenzi wezisebenzi.
\v 27 Kodwa lizanikela umnikelo wokutshiswa, kube luqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; amajongosi amabili amathole enkomo, inqama eyodwa, amawundlu ayisikhombisa alomnyaka owodwa\x + Levi 23.18,19.\x*.
\v 28 Lomnikelo wakho wokudla wempuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha, okuthathu kwetshumi ngejongosi elilodwa, lokubili kwetshumi ngenqama eyodwa,
\v 29 yilokho lalokho okwetshumi ngewundlu elilodwa, kumawundlu ayisikhombisa;
\v 30 izinyane lembuzi elilodwa, ukulenzela inhlawulo yokuthula\x + 28.15. 29.5. 28.22.\x*.
\v 31 Lizalungisa lokho ngaphandle komnikelo wokutshiswa ngezikhathi zonke, lomnikelo wakho wokudla (kube ngokungelasici kini) leminikelo yakho yokunathwayo\x + 28.19.\x*.